      • setElementType

        public GenericInstantiation.Builder setElementType(Type elementType)
        Type of the element parameter if the generic type instantiation is a GenericInstantiation.GenericType.LIST, GenericInstantiation.GenericType.OPTIONAL or GenericInstantiation.GenericType.SET. This property is optional and it is only relevant when the value of getGenericType() is one of GenericInstantiation.GenericType.LIST, GenericInstantiation.GenericType.OPTIONAL, or GenericInstantiation.GenericType.SET.
        Parameters:
        elementType - New value for the property.

      • setMapKeyType

        public GenericInstantiation.Builder setMapKeyType(Type mapKeyType)
        Type of the key parameter of the map generic type instantiation. The map generic type has a key parameter and value parameter. The type of the value parameter is described by GenericInstantiation.getMapValueType().. This property is optional and it is only relevant when the value of getGenericType() is GenericInstantiation.GenericType.MAP.
        Parameters:
        mapKeyType - New value for the property.

      • setMapValueType

        public GenericInstantiation.Builder setMapValueType(Type mapValueType)
        Type of the value parameter of the map generic type instantiation. The map generic type has a key parameter and value parameter. The type of the key parameter is described by GenericInstantiation.getMapKeyType().. This property is optional and it is only relevant when the value of getGenericType() is GenericInstantiation.GenericType.MAP.
        Parameters:
        mapValueType - New value for the property.
